God.&quot;—Prophets and </div><div class="t m362 x70 h30 y18bc ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Kings, </div><div class="t m1063 xac h4 y198d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pages 376, 377. </div><div class="t m1065 x78 h6c y1a38 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m5e3 x3d h6c y1a38 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What assurance did Jesus give </div><div class="t m2d5 x70 h6c y19cc ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His disciples when He gave the great </div><div class="t m7a0 x70 h6c y1fe2 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">commission? Matt. 28:18-20. Com-</div><div class="t m34a x70 h6c y6c4 ff1 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pare 1 John 3:24. </div><div class="t m2275 x1f h32 y1622 ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 46 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
